Macropis nuda & Dufourea novaeangliae SDM

Species Distribution Models (SDMs) for Macropis nuda and Dufourea novaeangliae created with MaxEnt using a 10th percentile threshold. All levels of suitability correspond to a prediction of species presence (Note: the presence threshold differs between each species). Red grid cells are predicted to be the most suitable given the available occurrence data and predictors used.

Approx. 1km resolution
